## 1️⃣ Domain-Based Features Created

| Feature | Formula | Business Meaning |
|---------|---------|-----------------|
| `spend_per_order` | total_spend ÷ orders | Avg basket size |
| `recency_score` | (1 - days_inactive/max) × 100 | How recent? (0-100) |
| `frequency_score` | orders/max × 100 | How often? (0-100) |
| `monetary_score` | spend/max × 100 | How much? (0-100) |
| `rfm_score` | 0.4×R + 0.35×M + 0.25×F | Overall value score |
| `customer_segment` | Cut on rfm_score | At Risk/Needs/Loyal/Champion |
| `churn_risk` | days_inactive > 60 | Binary churn flag |
| `is_high_value` | spend ≥ 75th percentile | Top spender flag |
| `engagement_score` | rating×10 + frequency/2 | Activity score |
| `age_group` | pd.cut on age | Generational segment |

