## ⚠️ Common Mistakes

- ❌ Label encoding for cities → ✅ One-hot (no order!)
- ❌ Not using `drop_first=True` → ✅ Dummy variable trap!
- ❌ Scaling tree models → ✅ Only scale for linear/SVM/NN
- ❌ fit_transform on test data → ✅ Only transform (fit on train!)
- ❌ Creating features after train/test split → ✅ Before split!

